            <span class="karpenter-badge">Karpenter NodePool</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tenant-ns-row">
            <span class="tenant-ns">tenant-a-dev</span>
            <span class="tenant-ns">tenant-a-staging</span>
            <span class="tenant-ns">tenant-a-prod</span>
          </div>
          <div class="argocd-note">
            ▸ Write: eks-tenant-a-write-role → tenant-a-* namespaces only &nbsp;|&nbsp; Karpenter: EC2NodeClass + NodePool via ArgoCD
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tenant-block">
          <div class="tenant-header">
            <span class="tenant-name">TENANT-B (team-beta)</span>
            <span class="karpenter-badge">Karpenter NodePool</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tenant-ns-row">
            <span class="tenant-ns">tenant-b-dev</span>
            <span class="tenant-ns">tenant-b-prod</span>
          </div>
          <div class="argocd-note">
            ▸ Write: eks-tenant-b-write-role → tenant-b-* namespaces only &nbsp;|&nbsp; Karpenter: EC2NodeClass + NodePool via ArgoCD
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tenant-block" style="border-color:rgba(100,116,139,0.2)">
          <div class="tenant-header">
            <span class="tenant-name" style="color:var(--text-dim)">TENANT-N (future)</span>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted)">
            Onboarded via platform ArgoCD — tenant creates PR to platform repo → platform team merges → NS + RBAC provisioned automatically
          </div>
