        Group: platform-readers
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rbac-card tenant-write">
      <div class="rbac-card-title">Tenant Write</div>
      <div class="rbac-kind">Role (NS-scoped) · Helm: tenant-rbac</div>
      <ul class="perm-list">
        <li class="perm-item">Full CRUD on own namespace resources</li>
        <li class="perm-item">Deployments, Services, Ingress</li>
        <li class="perm-item">ConfigMaps, Secrets (own NS)</li>
        <li class="perm-item">HPA, PodDisruptionBudget</li>
        <li class="perm-item">ServiceAccounts (own NS only)</li>
        <li class="perm-item">Pod exec, logs, port-forward</li>
        <li class="perm-item">❌ No platform NS access</li>
