          ▸ Resource quotas enforced per NS<br>
          ▸ OPA/Gatekeeper policy enforcement<br>
          ▸ Audit logs via CloudTrail + k8s audit<br>
          ▸ Secrets via External Secrets + ASM
        </div>
      </div>

